like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:40:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你班前線警唔洗咁落力做野㗎喎<br />\n因為領功都唔係你<br />\n真係情緒低落失控又驚落左order唔做野唔得<br />\n咪sick leave 囉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b4baf838e2963ec6e7d17d316b332edf556a03","tid":1247461,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"消耗同長久嘅佔領/圍堵似無用<br />\n但都同時消耗緊敵軍㗎<br />\n我地有嘅係200萬人民意<br />\n班保護權貴嘅警頂龍咪3萬幾<br />\n我地接力持久戰 間中衝下 間中成班人阻住條街<br />\n你話少人嘅佢地攰定我地可以輪流接力辛苦？<br />\n等佢地病嘅病 想辭職嘅辭職<br />\n我地覺得攰佢地都覺得攰<br />\n<br />\n不過認真 如果你係勇武派定和理非都好<br />\n如果你係呢兩星期不斷咁出黎 真係要識搵時間休息<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議大家商議接力嘅時間表</span><br />\n唔好咁快被打沉"},{"pid":"f6aa05d933b5636684e6a7e5afa62b862a646a3e","tid":1247461,"uid":228437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:53:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好灰心！眾怒難犯！自由萬歲！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"28f18e8efded5892294309b8ce19c401d00264b1","tid":1247461,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8a759edcfebb8755aac898d56a5fdd37a7cc2196","tid":1247461,"uid":261777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"33ed6b95678c520875bd1ccd4f70ba78c80b1c13","tid":1247461,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:59:10.000Z","msg":"驚比人拉嘅咪去到現場行行企企<br />\n如果覺得攰<br />\n覺得做嘅野開始無用<br />\n就幫下手做文宣<br />\n感化身邊嘅人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好睇少自己可以付出嘅多與少</span>"},{"pid":"17b3a1ce4a1fed2adfd85f0e34da575b9fe985ab","tid":1247461,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:05:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3b79f8fa93390637460ee5efe6ae8e39a684f03f","t